Upgrading Instructions for AweCrud
===============================

IMPORTANT

The following upgrading instructions are cumulative. That is,
if you want to upgrade from version A to version C and there is
version B between A and C, you need to follow the instructions
for both versions A and B.

General upgrade instructions
---------------------------
- Make a backup.
- Clean up your assets directory.
- Clean up your cache directory.
- Remove the "AweCrud" diretory from your application's extensions directory.
- Check the requirements of the new version in the README.md file.
- Then follow the install instructions for the new release in the INSTALL file.

Upgrading from 0.5
---------------------
No modification required.
